<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="cn"><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.3.3">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://quaner-dev.github.io/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml"/><link href="https://quaner-dev.github.io/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" hreflang="cn"/><updated>2024-03-10T08:41:07+00:00</updated><id>https://quaner-dev.github.io/feed.xml</id><title type="html">blank</title><subtitle>A technical blog about daily summaries. </subtitle><entry><title type="html">LVM简介</title><link href="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2024/LVM/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="LVM简介"/><published>2024-03-09T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2024-03-09T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2024/LVM</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2024/LVM/"><![CDATA[<h1 id="lvm简介">LVM简介</h1> <h2 id="一lvm概念">一、LVM概念</h2> <h3 id="1-pv">1. PV</h3> <p>PV（Physical Volume）：物理卷，即实际存在的硬盘，分区或者RAID</p> <h3 id="2-vg">2. VG</h3> <p>VG（Volume Group）：卷组，由多个物理卷组合成的整体卷组</p> <h3 id="3-lv">3. LV</h3> <p>LV（Logical Volume）：逻辑卷，从卷组中分割出来，可以挂载的逻辑存储卷</p> <h2 id="二lvm命令">二、LVM命令</h2> <table> <thead> <tr> <th>功能</th> <th>物理卷管理</th> <th>卷组管理</th> <th>逻辑卷管理</th> </tr> </thead> <tbody> <tr> <td>扫描</td> <td>pvscan</td> <td>vgscan</td> <td>lvscan</td> </tr> <tr> <td>建立</td> <td>pvcreate</td> <td>vgcreate</td> <td>lvcreate</td> </tr> <tr> <td>显示</td> <td>pvdisplay</td> <td>vgdisplay</td> <td>lvdisplay</td> </tr> <tr> <td>删除</td> <td>pvremote</td> <td>vgremote</td> <td>lvremove</td> </tr> <tr> <td>扩展</td> <td>物理卷无法扩展</td> <td>vgextend</td> <td>lvextend</td> </tr> <tr> <td>缩小</td> <td>物理卷无法缩小</td> <td>vgreduce</td> <td>lvreduce</td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <h2 id="三lvm实战">三、LVM实战</h2> <h3 id="1-pvcreate">1. pvcreate</h3> <p><img src="/assets/img/blog_preview/2024-03-09-LVM/pvcreate.png" alt="pvcreate"/></p> <h3 id="2-pvremove">2. pvremove</h3> <p><img src="/assets/img/blog_preview/2024-03-09-LVM/pvremove.png" alt="pvremove"/></p> <h3 id="3-vgcreate">3. vgcreate</h3> <p><img src="/assets/img/blog_preview/2024-03-09-LVM/vgcreate.png" alt="vgcreate"/></p> <h3 id="4-vgremove">4. vgremove</h3> <p><img src="/assets/img/blog_preview/2024-03-09-LVM/vgremove.png" alt="vgremove"/></p> <h3 id="5-lvcreate">5. lvcreate</h3> <p><img src="/assets/img/blog_preview/2024-03-09-LVM/lvcreate.png" alt="lvcreate"/></p> <h3 id="6-lvremove">6. lvremove</h3> <p><img src="/assets/img/blog_preview/2024-03-09-LVM/lvremove.png" alt="lvremove"/></p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="LVM"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[介绍LVM使用]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Storcli使用文档</title><link href="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2023/Storcli%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Storcli使用文档"/><published>2023-11-24T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2023-11-24T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2023/Storcli%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2023/Storcli%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3/"><![CDATA[<h1 id="storcli使用文档">Storcli使用文档</h1> <h2 id="storcli安装地址">Storcli安装地址</h2> <p><a href="https://www.broadcom.com/site-search?q=Latest%20Storcli">Storcli安装包</a></p> <h2 id="操作手册">操作手册</h2> <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># Ubuntu安装Storcli包</span>
dpkg <span class="nt">-i</span> xxx.deb

<span class="c"># Centos安装Storcli包</span>
rmp <span class="nt">-i</span> xxx.rpm

<span class="c"># 查看raid信息</span>
/opt/MegaRAID/storcli/storcli64 /c0 show all
</code></pre></div></div>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="raid"/><category term="storcli"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Storcli简介]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">ubuntu下载离线安装包</title><link href="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2023/ubuntu%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E7%A6%BB%E7%BA%BF%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8C%85/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="ubuntu下载离线安装包"/><published>2023-11-24T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2023-11-24T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2023/ubuntu%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E7%A6%BB%E7%BA%BF%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8C%85</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2023/ubuntu%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E7%A6%BB%E7%BA%BF%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8C%85/"><![CDATA[<h1 id="ubuntu下载离线安装包">ubuntu下载离线安装包</h1> <h2 id="一查询依赖列表">一、查询依赖列表</h2> <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># 查询依赖列表</span>
<span class="c"># 替换&lt;packagename&gt;为需要安装的包</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-cache depends <span class="nt">--recurse</span> <span class="nt">--no-recommends</span> <span class="nt">--no-suggests</span> <span class="nt">--no-conflicts</span> <span class="nt">--no-breaks</span> <span class="nt">--no-replaces</span> <span class="nt">--no-enhances</span> &lt;packagename&gt; | <span class="nb">grep</span> <span class="s2">"^</span><span class="se">\w</span><span class="s2">"</span> | <span class="nb">sort</span> <span class="nt">-u</span>
</code></pre></div></div> <h2 id="二下载离线安装包">二、下载离线安装包</h2> <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># 下载离线安装包</span>
<span class="c"># 替换&lt;packagename&gt;为需要安装的包</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>apt-get download <span class="si">$(</span>apt-cache depends <span class="nt">--recurse</span> <span class="nt">--no-recommends</span> <span class="nt">--no-suggests</span> <span class="nt">--no-conflicts</span> <span class="nt">--no-breaks</span> <span class="nt">--no-replaces</span> <span class="nt">--no-enhances</span> &lt;packagename&gt; | <span class="nb">grep</span> <span class="s2">"^</span><span class="se">\w</span><span class="s2">"</span> | <span class="nb">sort</span> <span class="nt">-u</span><span class="si">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div> <h2 id="三下载安装包">三、下载安装包</h2> <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo </span>apt <span class="nb">install</span> <span class="nt">-d</span> &lt;packagename&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="apt"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[ubuntu下载离线安装包]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">ubuntu设置root用户登录</title><link href="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2023/ubuntu%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEroot%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="ubuntu设置root用户登录"/><published>2023-11-24T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2023-11-24T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2023/ubuntu%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEroot%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2023/ubuntu%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEroot%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95/"><![CDATA[<h1 id="ubuntu设置root用户登录">ubuntu设置root用户登录</h1> <h2 id="一设置root用户密码">一、设置root用户密码</h2> <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># 设置root用户密码</span>
<span class="c"># 输入两次root用户密码，最终返回password updated successfully，则表示密码设定成功</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>passwd root
</code></pre></div></div> <h2 id="二设置root用户登录">二、设置root用户登录</h2> <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># 修改sshd配置文件</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>vim /etc/ssh/sshd_config

<span class="c"># 反注释PermitRootLogin，并修改参数为yes</span>
PermitRootLogin <span class="nb">yes</span>
<span class="c"># 反注释PasswordAuthentication，并修改参数为yes</span>
PasswordAuthentication <span class="nb">yes</span>

<span class="c"># 按ESC，保存sshd_config</span>
:wq
</code></pre></div></div> <h2 id="三重启ssh服务">三、重启SSH服务</h2> <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c"># 重启ssh服务</span>
<span class="nb">sudo </span>systemctl restart sshd
</code></pre></div></div> <h2 id="四root用户登录测试">四、root用户登录测试</h2> <p>使用root账户直接登录服务器，登录成功则完成设置</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="ssh"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[ubuntu设定root登录]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">常用ES操作汇总</title><link href="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2023/%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8ES%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%B1%87%E6%80%BB/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="常用ES操作汇总"/><published>2023-11-24T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2023-11-24T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2023/%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8ES%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%B1%87%E6%80%BB</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2023/%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8ES%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%B1%87%E6%80%BB/"><![CDATA[<h1 id="常用es操作汇总">常用ES操作汇总</h1> <h2 id="一查询es数据">一、查询ES数据</h2> <p>URL：<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">http://IP:PORT/person_dynamic/_search</code></p> <div class="language-json highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"query"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="nl">"bool"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
      </span><span class="nl">"must"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">[</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
          </span><span class="nl">"range"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
            </span><span class="nl">"captureTime"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
              </span><span class="nl">"gt"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"2023-08-16 13:00:00"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
              </span><span class="nl">"lt"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"2023-08-16 13:10:00"</span><span class="w">
            </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
          </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
      </span><span class="p">]</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div></div> <h2 id="二删除es数据">二、删除ES数据</h2> <p>URL：<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">http://IP:PORT/person_dynamic/_delete_by_query</code></p> <div class="language-json highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="nl">"query"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="nl">"bool"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
      </span><span class="nl">"must"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">[</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
          </span><span class="nl">"range"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
            </span><span class="nl">"captureTime"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
              </span><span class="nl">"gt"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"2023-08-16 13:00:00"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
              </span><span class="nl">"lt"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s2">"2023-08-16 13:10:00"</span><span class="w">
            </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
          </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
      </span><span class="p">]</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
  </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div></div> <h2 id="三查询索引结构">三、查询索引结构</h2> <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>curl <span class="nt">--location</span> <span class="s1">'http://IP:PORT/test04/_mapping'</span>
</code></pre></div></div> <h2 id="四查询所有索引库">四、查询所有索引库</h2> <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>curl <span class="nt">--location</span> <span class="s1">'http://IP:PORT/_cat/indices'</span>
</code></pre></div></div>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="elasticsearch"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[ES命令汇总]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Displaying External Posts on Your al-folio Blog</title><link href="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2022/displaying-external-posts-on-your-al-folio-blog/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Displaying External Posts on Your al-folio Blog"/><published>2022-04-23T23:20:09+00:00</published><updated>2022-04-23T23:20:09+00:00</updated><id>https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2022/displaying-external-posts-on-your-al-folio-blog</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://quaner-dev.github.io/blog/2022/displaying-external-posts-on-your-al-folio-blog/"><![CDATA[]]></content><author><name></name></author></entry></feed>